Bring-your-own credentials
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

BoB is a consumer application that you run on your own machine with your own
credentials. It does not bundle, proxy, or resell access to any model provider.
Each backend (Anthropic, OpenAI, Google, Z.AI, Moonshot/Kimi, MiniMax, DeepSeek,
local model servers, etc.) is reached with your own API key or your own official
vendor CLI logged in under your own subscription, per each vendor's published
terms. See COMPLIANCE.md for details.

BoB depends on third-party open-source software, each under its own license.
Those licenses are retained in the respective packages' distributions.
